 />\n出一本屬於香港人嘅自由之書<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1359361\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1359361</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"094368eb87e11b6c4a1c9292145f292c9d92c7b8","tid":1367582,"uid":276020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T10:03:36.000Z","msg":"不會放棄"},{"pid":"e27f3ac7259e9343f3fedde4e2134995da78795a","tid":1367582,"uid":276020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T10:38:22.000Z","msg":"沙田友"},{"pid":"fe81c14726a22bb6d0fddf3f1966a862b8e3b940","tid":1367582,"uid":258927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T10:38:47.000Z","msg":"兄弟爬山, 做乜都好, 搵咗攻略睇先! <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔好再on 99 講有事退去寫字樓! <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">元朗有L寫字樓/商場你退!!! </span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nif 天水被人圍咗, 無交通工具, 跑online 離開元朗去洪水橋/屯門要行 1.5 至 2 小時! <br />\n即係<span style=\"color: blue;\">2倍老銅出支聯辦既距離</span>!<br />\n<br />\n我見好多兄弟仲未意識到<span style=\"color: red;\">鄉村同城巿既分別</span>!!!<br />\n做乜都好, 睇路呀!!! 唔好去送頭呀!!!<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EzULh8v.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEzULh8v.png&h=28fe2795&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n地圖傳送門:<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1361703/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1361703/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"d5772ce77ea1f46e618b5ba60f1a339db1288fbb","tid":1367582,"uid":276020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T12:06:54.000Z","msg":"推"}]}